<subSubSection pageId="100" pageNumber="379" type="reference_group">
<paragraph blockId="100.[2067,2662,1754,2177]" pageId="100" pageNumber="379">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[2068,2224,1754,1783]" pageId="100" pageNumber="379">Taxonomy.</emphasis>
<taxonomicName authority="Burt, 1932" authorityName="Burt" authorityYear="1932" class="Mammalia" family="Cricetidae" genus="Peromyscus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Rodentia" pageId="100" pageNumber="379" phylum="Chordata" rank="subSpecies" species="guardia" subSpecies="interparietalis">Peromyscus guardia interparietalis Burt, 1932</taxonomicName>
, 
<materialsCitation ID-GBIF-Occurrence="3818814811" pageId="100" pageNumber="379">“South San Lorenzo Island (latitude 28° 36’ N., longitude 112° 51’ W.), Gulf of California, Mexico.”</materialsCitation>
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="100" pageNumber="379" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="100.[2067,2662,1754,2177]" pageId="100" pageNumber="379">
Although several morphological studies support specific status of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Burt" authorityYear="1932" box="[2442,2654,1947,1980]" class="Mammalia" family="Cricetidae" genus="Peromyscus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Rodentia" pageId="100" pageNumber="379" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="interparietalis">P. interparietalis</taxonomicName>
, recent evidence suggests that it might be a subspecies of 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Baird" baseAuthorityYear="1857" box="[2288,2429,2030,2059]" class="Mammalia" family="Cricetidae" genus="Peromyscus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Rodentia" pageId="100" pageNumber="379" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="eremicus">P. eremicus</taxonomicName>
. 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Burt" authorityYear="1932" class="Mammalia" family="Cricetidae" genus="Peromyscus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Rodentia" pageId="100" pageNumber="379" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="interparietalis">Peromyscus interparietalis</taxonomicName>
is in the 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Baird" baseAuthorityYear="1857" box="[2336,2441,2069,2098]" class="Mammalia" family="Cricetidae" genus="Peromyscus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Rodentia" pageId="100" pageNumber="379" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="eremicus">eremicus</taxonomicName>
species group. Three subspecies recognized.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
